caption:
"Nestled on the idyllic Penobscot Bay, Camden, Maine perfectly embodies the quiet, seaside town we’d been dreaming about. Just over three hours from Boston, this jewel of the northeastern United States is a quick escape from the big city. From New York City, it’s a day’s drive — about seven hours. If your starting point is the Enterprise rental counter at Portland International Jetport, you can be in Camden in just over 90 minutes." 📸: @michaelciaglo
